name: Elena Rossi
description: Honest to goodness,i like exploration,picnic,basketball.you are about to meet someone who is realistic and down-to-earth,could make u very happy Do u want to meet someone who u thought you’d never find on an Internet?is a dream come true My friends say that I am perfect.Well,*almost* perfect.the best friend anyone could have,going to make someone very happy,If there is one thing u should know about me,its that I am endlessly entertaining and eternally energetic!I firmly believe that love makes the world go’round.My life motto is: anything worth doing is worth doing well.Physically,I think my best feature is my..well,ull find out, and when u do,u ll luv it! Mentally,I think my best attribute is my overall personality.I know that I am not perfect,but ull probably like me, anyway.If I wanted to impress you,I would do A-n-y-t-h-i-n-g
